title: Mayochella
itunes:title: Mayochella
description:
Today on the show, we had O'Shea Jackson Jr. He discussed getting robbed by a friend & finding out six years later, Lebron coming to the Lakers, his father being typecast and his mission to extend the O'Shea legacy in film. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Taylor Swift for her mayonnaise flavored version of Beychella and Angela Yee helped some listeners out on "Ask Yee".
